Type of Feat: General
You have mastered a wide range of slashing weapons.  Your training with one specific weapon now extends to other weapons of a similar sort.
Prerequisites: BAB +8, Weapon Specialization with a slashing weapon.
Benefit: When using any slashing weapon, you gain a +2 bonus on attacks and a +2 bonus on damage.
Special: A fighter can choose Melee Weapon Mastery (Slashing) as one of his fighter bonus feats.